# NETWORK::NETWORK_SESSION_KICK_PLAYER

## Summary
Kicks the given player from the session. Callable only by the host

## Parameters
* **PLAYER_INDEX** netPlayerID

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Only works as host.
